en_388550_7	It will be 615 meters long.
en_388550_8	Another tunnel with a length of 268 meters will be built at Bambarenda on this rail track.
en_388550_9	The main railway station at Beliatta has a length of 300 meters and it will have three platforms.
en_388550_10	Underground tunnels will be made for the passengers to move across the platforms of the station.
en_388550_11	Plans have been drawn up to construct underground tunnels at the four main railway stations.
en_388550_12	The railway track will be built across the Nilwala River.
en_388550_13	Therefore a bridge with a length of 1037 meters will be built across the Nilwala River.
